%% KubeRay Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MutWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant ValWH as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant RCC as RayCluster Controller
    participant AuthC as Auth Controller
    participant MTLSC as mTLS Controller
    participant NPC as NetworkPolicy Controller
    participant RJC as RayJob Controller
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Workers as Ray Workers<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation with Authentication

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create RayCluster<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>MutWH: Admission Review (CREATE)<br/>TLS / Webhook cert
    MutWH-->>K8sAPI: Patched: enableSecureTrustedNetwork=true,<br/>enableIngress=false
    K8sAPI->>ValWH: Admission Review (CREATE)<br/>TLS / Webhook cert
    ValWH-->>K8sAPI: Allowed
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayCluster created

    RCC->>K8sAPI: Create head pod, worker pods, services<br/>ServiceAccount token
    AuthC->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute in platform namespace<br/>ServiceAccount token
    AuthC->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant in cluster namespace<br/>ServiceAccount token
    AuthC->>K8sAPI: Inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar into head pod<br/>ServiceAccount token
    MTLSC->>CertMgr: Create Issuer + Certificate CRs<br/>ServiceAccount token
    CertMgr-->>MTLSC: CA + TLS secrets provisioned
    NPC->>K8sAPI: Create head + worker NetworkPolicies<br/>ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 2: User Accesses Ray Dashboard

    User->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}<br/>HTTPS / Bearer Token
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>HTTP / internal
    RBAC->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / SA token
    K8sAPI-->>RBAC: Auth OK
    RBAC->>RayHead: Proxy to dashboard<br/>HTTP / localhost / plaintext
    RayHead-->>RBAC: Dashboard response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Dashboard HTML

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 3: RayJob Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create RayJob<br/>Bearer Token
    RJC->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster (if needed)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    RJC->>RayHead: Submit job via dashboard API<br/>HTTP 8265/TCP / plaintext
    RJC->>K8sAPI: Create submitter Job<br/>ServiceAccount token
    RayHead->>Workers: Distribute tasks<br/>gRPC 10001/TCP / mTLS (if enabled)
    Workers-->>RayHead: Task results<br/>gRPC / mTLS
    RayHead-->>RJC: Job status
